- (void) confLogEntry: (NSString *)  message
withSeverity: (int)  severity 

Log event handler to be implemented by the delegate of the ICAdministration object.

The log messages can be filtered based on their severities. These are defined within the SEVERITY_LOG_LEVELS enumeration and can be converted to a human readable form using the severityLevelString and severityLevelStringA methods of the ICISMPDevice class.

Parameters
messageThe log message
severityThe severity of the log message
- (void) confSerialData: (NSData *)  data
incoming: (BOOL)  isIncoming

Parameters

isIncomingA boolean for the direction in/out of the serial data
